{"tid":1855502,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有無人知武漢肺炎病人點好返？","createTime":"2020-02-01T06:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T07:30:15.000Z","uid":167585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d6b9c0484c18a60cdc1018b3d09d1622b183e7","tid":1855502,"uid":167585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:25:07.000Z","msg":"醫到啦咩？"},{"pid":"b771b66e6ac72088400bce8248655ae400ffb097","tid":1855502,"uid":167585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎大爆發，疫情遍佈全國。廣東省政府下午宣佈，已做好應急預案，在廣州、深圳、珠海、佛山、東莞等市建設臨時醫院的準備。中國國家衞健委今天舉行記者會表示，由於抗體持續時間可能不夠長的因素，武漢肺炎患者<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">痊癒</span></span>後還是有再次感染的風險，因此治癒的患者也應加強防護。本港感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷向《蘋果》表示，如何界定「康復」成疑問，武漢肺炎康復者應更注意個人衞生，既排除二次感染風險，亦防止病毒「未清」而感染他人。此外，浙江有專家指出，新型冠狀病毒不排除母嬰垂直傳播風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200131/5CDW3KU3Y2UPS76MCLPFMYT4GQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200131%2F5CDW3KU3Y2UPS76MCLPFMYT4GQ%2F&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Io429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=380edc2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200131%2F5CDW3KU3Y2UPS76MCLPFMYT4GQ%2F&h=59916cbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200131/5CDW3KU3Y2UPS76MCLPFMYT4GQ/</a>"},{"pid":"761e4f14e023f03e47c325fbd464e72f1e4e557f","tid":1855502,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"靠自身抵抗力啦<br />\n同埋我估大部係係後生啦<br />\n老果D就大機會等死多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cbd7410e5a9a24fafd19eaaacb52c328ff4933","tid":1855502,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"病唔死咪好lo<br />\n病結局唔係死就係好"},{"pid":"d7837265fe46fdc0c16aedbc718160da4c9bdc7d","tid":1855502,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07: